  m_text: "Welcome challenger, you are now located in the Trial Chambers. In order
    to reach your goal you must traverse the two preparatory chambers and overcome
    the final challenge at the end. Your courage to take this journey impressed me
    and so I've left you my grappling hook for you to use. \r\nEach Trial Chamber
    is harder than the last.\nGood luck, challenger."
